channel.title: [z508] The Ancient Edgeville Massacre [z508]
channel.description:
[CENTER][B]This source is basically the original server created by Zach, which was later edited by Owner J.[/b] [size=24pt][B][U]CREDITS[/U][/B] ZACH - 90% OWNER J - 9.99% ME - 0.001%[/size]
[b]There isn't a specific client, it will run with any, for best game-play, use Umair's IP Changer.
I've changed the names, added a few commands, and fixed a few bugs.
Basically I've leached it, but who cares? This source, I believe is popular, meaning some people want it, but, can't find it, that's the main reason I'm posting this.[/B]
[B][U]Features I've added[/U][/B] Removed Dragon halberd special, was too glitchy. Dragon dagger accuracy increased. Magic shortbow accuracy increased. Armadyl godsword strength increased. Perfected dharok, will now hit 99 under the right circumstances, but VERY rare. Fixed godsword specials, increased accuracy, Armadyl & Bandos have been powered up. Barrelchest anchor overall increased. Special & non special. Dragon mace special accuracy increased, but slightly powered down. The void magic set effect now actually works. (Before it didn't). [B]Basically I've just improved the PKing.[/B]
[B][U]Added a few commands~[/U][/B] ::magicrunes - Gives 1,000 of every kind of rune. ::barragerunes - 1,000 barrages. ::vengeancerunes - 1,000 vengeances. ::runepk - Gives the old school Rune PKing gear. And a few others that I can't remember, from the top of my head.
